<Layout title="Structural Warranty and Construction Defect Liability When Selling a Newly Built Brisbane Home 2026 | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Selling a Brisbane home inside the QBCC home warranty period or builder defects liability period? Here is what transfers to the buyer, what you must disclose under the Property Law Act 2023, and how to keep the deal clean." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
